{"word":"ὑποθήκη","slug":"ὑποθήκη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποθήκη</b></el> <el>(ὑποθήκη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὑποτίθημι'><el>ὑποτίθημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a suggestion, counsel, warning, piece of advice</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a pledge, a mortgage</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}